  "title": "Pronouncing Pronouns, Be Verbs, and Contractions",
  "learningGoal": "The learner will accurately pronounce the nuanced differences between long form combinations (I am, You are) and fluid spoken contractions (I'm, You're), and successfully execute the voiced 'th' sound in 'They'.",
