  "instructions": "In natural spoken English, words are often mashed together into contractions. Listen closely to the difference between 'I am' and 'I'm'. You will practice 16 different phrases. Use your microphone to mirror the native speaker exactly.",
  "contentItems": [
    {
      "type": "note",
      "text": "Focus heavily on the 'th' sound in They and Them. It is a vibrating 'द' sound."
    }
  ],
